Package command

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Command
    A abstract command to be inherited by specific commands Contains the generic method to be polymorphic.
    Command_AddDeadline
    Specific type of command that add deadline task to the storage.
    Command_AddEvent
    Specific type of command that add event task to the storage.
    Command_AddTask
    Generic command to add a new task.
    Command_AddToDo
    Specific type of command that add to do task to the storage.
    Command_Delete
    Specific command to delete a task based on index.
    Command_Done
    Specific command to mark the task as done.
    Command_Exit
    Specific command to exit the programme.
    Command_Find
    Specific command to find task that has the keyword
    Command_List
    Specific command that display the list of task.
    Command_Reset
    Specific command that reset the storage.
